      <item>
        <title>Categories does not display items</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mburridge]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/kasper">@kasper</a></p>
<p>Add this to the <code>state.source</code> section of <code>frontity.settings.js</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="lang-javascript">"taxonomies": [
  {
    taxonomy: "category",
    endpoint: "categories",
    postTypeEndpoint: "blogg",
  },
]
</code></pre>
<p><a href="https://api.frontity.org/frontity-packages/features-packages/wp-source#state-source-taxonomies">See here</a> for more info.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/categories-does-not-display-items/4595/12">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
        <link>https://community.frontity.org/t/categories-does-not-display-items/4595/12</link>
